data.description: Nestled in Cape Coral, Florida, this 3-bed, 2-bath home is a 1,398 sq ft retreat, offering the perfect blend of comfort and coastal living. The open floor plan seamlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas, creating an ideal space for gatherings. The bedrooms are well-appointed, and the master suite features an ensuite bathroom. With a shimmering pool in the backyard and a screened-in lanai, outdoor living is elevated. Additionally, the property's proximity to a boat ramp caters to water enthusiasts, making it a dream for boating and fishing lovers. Situated in the coveted Cape Coral community, this home provides easy access to parks, nature preserves, and the vibrant local culture. Experience the essence of coastal living in this inviting residence, where comfort meets style against the backdrop of Florida's Gulf Coast charm. *** NEW ROOF 2019*** SEE 360 VIRTUAL TOUR***
